          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-03-29T18:40:32Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>RPPA Commercial Recreation Concessions Pilot Program Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Recreation and Public Purposes Act to direct the Department of the Interior to establish a pilot program that authorizes commercial recreation concessions on land patented or leased under the Act.</p> <p>Interior shall enter into at least 10 agreements with parties to whom such land has been patented or leased for the establishment of these concessions. </p> <p>A party to such an agreement may enter into agreements with third parties to establish such concessions. </p>]]></text>
